But there's a nascent new industry here in

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:17.845
Silicon Valley and around the world that looks into

00:00:17.845 --> 00:00:24.015
flight as a transportation medium for goods and people on a daily basis.

00:00:24.015 --> 00:00:26.730
Now, we have the chance here at Udacity in Silicon Valley,

00:00:26.730 --> 00:00:28.710
