00:00:35.870 --> 00:00:38.485
It's become the biggest topic in Silicon Valley today.

00:00:38.485 --> 00:00:40.530
I predict in five years time,

00:00:40.530 --> 00:00:44.865
flying vehicles will be the biggest topic in Silicon Valley innovation.

00:00:44.865 --> 00:00:46.605
And the reason I believe is this,

00:00:46.605 --> 00:00:49.095
transportation is a huge industry,

00:00:49.095 --> 00:00:51.287
really important for people,

00:00:51.287 --> 00:00:55.182
but the ground is very limited in transportation.

00:00:55.182 --> 00:00:56.750
If we could build vehicles,

00:00:56.750 --> 00:00:58.995
it would easy to go off vertically,

00:00:58.995 --> 00:01:01.285
fly us to where we want to go, and land.

00:01:01.285 --> 00:01:04.065
