00:01:09.245 --> 00:01:13.505
And we will be environmentally more friendly and use less energy.

00:01:13.505 --> 00:01:16.850
And the last thing is a bit of a surprise but if you look at the modern aircraft,

00:01:16.850 --> 00:01:18.795
when a modern aircraft loses its power,

00:01:18.795 --> 00:01:22.695
it glides down at a glide ratio of about one-to-15 or so,.

00:01:22.695 --> 00:01:28.590
which means, the energy consumption used for lift for keeping a flying vehicle in the air

00:01:28.590 --> 00:01:34.611
is only a 15th of the energy used to combat the air, which is what we call drag.

00:01:34.611 --> 00:01:38.850
